{"tid":1986972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復立法會- 而家未肯定35+, 可唔可以幫我推呢一個行動post","createTime":"2020-04-24T07:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T07:28:41.000Z","uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a639e896a5e9dd3799d0362b6dce14f6a295ea24","tid":1986972,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"呢個ig有嚟緊dse主科邊度考嘅資訊， 希望大家去返近自己屋企嘅學校派選民登記表， 呢度可能幾百幾千票<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_SS9hxBqWD/?igshid=vengbiy843fl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_SS9hxBqWD%2F%3Figshid%3Dvengbiy843fl&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=ad394bd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_SS9hxBqWD%2F%3Figshid%3Dvengbiy843fl&h=03324ce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B_SS9hxBqWD/?igshid=vengbiy843fl</a><br />\n<br />\n估計大約有3萬名校生今年滿18歲<br />\n希望各位幫本土派議員盡量爭取多一票<br />\n立法會選民登記截止日期2020年5月2日， 我哋大概只係得五日可以行動<br />\n<br />\n詳細考試日期<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Exam_Timetable/2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FHKDSE%2FExam_Timetable%2F2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=af838eb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Exam_Timetable/2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf</a><br />\n試場查詢<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2FHKDSE%2Fadmin%2Fexam_centres%2Fexam_centres.html&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=d052b3fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html</a><br />\n<br />\n建議大家自行<br />\n印有QRcode單張 +派選民登記表格<br />\n可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=34bf9a3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：<br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民<br />\n選民登記填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=575cdfcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=4252ed4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=586e2264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位等考生考完之後 先派選民登記表， 費事打亂佢哋嘅節奏<br />\n<br />\n行動有違反限聚令嘅風險， 請到場考生配合， 話手足係自己師兄一齊溫書之類"}]}